Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.77,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'd sort of casually met
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.77,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nanigenaku deatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.77,0:00:33.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering kindness together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.77,0:00:33.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yasashisa yoseatte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.67,0:00:36.44,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The hide-and-seek continues
