Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.21,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wanna sell your soul
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.88,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a fancy yellow touch
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.88,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shareta kiiroi tatchi de
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.88,0:00:46.21,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget smile again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be dancing always
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo odotteitai dake
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.62,0:00:55.62,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chase me, chase me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.62,0:00:55.62,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee oikakete oikakete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White breeze
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroi kaze
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.49,0:01:01.80,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want it to be a crush, then love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.49,0:01:01.80,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee koi ni natte ai ni natte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.33,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spread my wings
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.33,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hane hirogetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.33,0:01:07.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take the good things and the bad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.33,0:01:07.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee ii koto mo warui koto mo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.14,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add them all together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.14,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subete tashite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.14,0:01:13.68,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divide it by two and live well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.14,0:01:13.68,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ni de watte umaku ikite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.68,0:01:21.61,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to transcend time
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.68,0:01:21.61,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toki o koetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.26,0:01:36.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meškáš, Touma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne! Kumagoro je naštvaný!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte.\NZdržal som sa v práci.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prezident je vždy zaneprázdnený.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ty, Noriko?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dúfam, že si nemala problém\Ntak náhle pricestovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.58,0:01:55.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V pohode. Na Ryuho detské\Npožiadavky som si už zvykla.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si krutá!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už ma nemáš rada, Noriko?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.69,0:02:02.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To by som si nedovolila.\NPreto som tu, vieš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže s tým súhlasíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme.\NZdá sa, že to bude zaujímavé.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude! Pretože je tam zábavný chlapík!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:17.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že ten chlapík\Nmá schopnosť ovplyvňovať druhých.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, o kom to hovoríte?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čoskoro sa s ním stretneš.\NČoskoro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, idem do práce!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, dokedy tu plánuješ bývať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínam si, že by som ti dovolil...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.79,0:02:40.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak! Tento nový byt je tak veľký.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A navyše, ty si ma\Nsem priviezol, spomínaš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta! To bola chyba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, ja idem... cmuk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten sviniar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zaujímavé.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netušil som, že máš\Ntak šteklivé uši, Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu dočerta robíš?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priniesol som darček.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že Shindo\Nje opäť plný energie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seguchi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mohol by si ma\Noslovovať krsným menom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cestou späť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...som mu povedal o svojej minulosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel to vedieť,\Ntak som mu povedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som sa ho zbaviť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snažil som sa ho nenávidieť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nikdy nechcem byť nikým milovaný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.63,0:03:49.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nikdy na to nechcem spomínať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale spomenul si si na to, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.14,0:04:05.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že Shindo nebol\Njedinou obeťou tohto incidentu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Postarám sa, aby za to Aizawa zaplatil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ešte stále tu vysedávate?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnešné interview je príležitosť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ako zviditeľniť váš singel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezabudnite sa usmievať\Na ukázať dobrý imidž.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vieme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, Shuichi, poďme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.31,0:04:35.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale dnes chcem ísť\Nskôr domov za Yukim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choďte bezomňa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asi to nepôjde.\NBudem sa snažiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý chlapec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebude to interview o Shuichiho\Nvzťahu s Yukim, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadny strachy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.59,0:04:55.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Upozornil som ich,\Naby túto tému nespomínali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že ste na našej strane.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie je to úžasné?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebol z toho žiaden škandál...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a jeho popularita u fanúšikov stúpla.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy keď niečo vyvedie,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,každý mu to záhadne odpustí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, na čo čakáš?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Necháme ťa tu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bežím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Záhadne, huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tatchi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vôbec ho to nepoložilo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.97,0:05:37.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tatchi, vykašli sa naňho.\NPrečo ťa ten Shindo stále trápi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy nedovolím, aby si niekto\Nako on na mňa otváral ústa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tatchi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki! Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.86,0:06:04.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže pokračujete vo vašom nahrávaní?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.73,0:06:08.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, je to náš prvý singel,\Ntakže by sme radi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmiete sem ísť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koná sa tu interview!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darebák jeden!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To nesmiete, pán K! To je preda...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ti niečo povedať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš odo mňa ešte niečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám v úmysle sa nechať\Ntakto zosmiešňovať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Príde vás to draho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj tak nič nezmôžeš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tie oči...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rovnako ako predtým...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten pohľad...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žeby si skutočne dokázal niekoho zabiť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No a?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.75,0:06:57.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pýtam sa, čo ak som dokázal, Aizawa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prídem na to! Nájdem tvoju slabinu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Za každú cenu, ty a Shindo budete...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty hnusný, špinavý podrazák!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si dovoluješ\Ndotknúť sa môjho Yukiho?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môjho Yukiho! Môjho Yukiho! Môjho...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daj pokoj s tvojím Yukim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nauč sa otvárať dvere, ty sopliak!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Len som sa sem nasťahoval\Na už si to tu rozbil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.78,0:07:31.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Letel som ti na pomoc,\Nako to môžeš povedať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto ťa neprosil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čože??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty, ty, ty, ty, ty, ty, ty,\Nty, ty, ty, ty, ty, ty, ty!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta, Yuki Eiri!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta, Yuki Eiri!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zistím si o tebe všetko\Na predhodím to médiam!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To bude tvoj koniec!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, najväčší strach\Nz toho máš ty. Keď uvidíš...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.57,0:07:50.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.94,0:07:51.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.31,0:07:55.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jediná vec, na ktorú sa zmôžeš,\Naby si vyhral...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...tak ťa úprimne ľutujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dočerta! Robia zo mňa hlupáka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To im neprejde.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som, že budeš mať viac inteligencie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som veľmi sklamaný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seguchi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, si v poriadku?\NNie je ti nič?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal ti niečo nepríjemné?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spravil ti niečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si ten, komu ublížil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ale už som v poriadku...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to moja chyba!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli mne si...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,prežil rovnaké utrpenie,\Nako kedysi ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yuki?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úprimne, chcel som byť s tebou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemohol som...\NNechcel som si spomenúť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spomenúť, ako ma vtedy zneužili.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stačilo! Už nikdy sa to nesmie stať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nikdy sa tam nechcem vrátiť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal si Shinda nechať napokoji.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A nerobiť zbytočné hlúposti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.73,0:09:23.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy som netušil,\Nže zájdeš tak ďaleko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.46,0:09:27.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by si ostal ticho sedieť,\Nmohol si mať pred sebou sľubnú budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Č-Čo to dočerta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.07,0:09:34.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keďže si sa pustil do Yukiho Eiriho,\Ndraho za to zaplatíš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si ho stále zastávaš?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.25,0:09:44.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Eiriho milujem viac\Nnež kohokoľvek na svete.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zbohom, Aizawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto ťa nezradí,\Na nikomu nedovolím, aby ti ublížil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ochránim ťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni! Bolí ma z teba hlava.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.42,0:10:20.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...! Snažím sa vymyslieť niečo,\Nčím by som ťa povzbudil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.22,0:10:24.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buď ticho! Neplakal som 6 rokov,\Nhlava mi ide prasknúť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6 rokov?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si úžasný!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja plačem aspoň raz denne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bože, to je super!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akoby si mal temnú minulosť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkať, vlastne máš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aké prehlásenie chcete vydať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...po náhlom zastavení\Naktivít skupiny ASK,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,prezident Seguchi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.62,0:10:57.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, dnes tu nie som ako prezident N-G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja, Touma Seguchi, Ryuichi\NSakuma a Noriko Ukai,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,opäť založíme skupinu Nittle Grasper,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ktorú sme zrušili pred troma rokmi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne?! Skutočne?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opäť bude Nittle Grasper?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisaki, ty si o tom vedel?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, netušil som to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, opäť budeme môcť\Npočuť Nittle Grasper!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.25,0:11:29.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám pre vás ďalšie dobré správy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.49,0:11:33.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je váš K! Bývalý Ryuichiho manažér!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S fantastickými známosťami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vybavil som pre Bad Luck účasť\Nv hudobnom programe "Hit Stage".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V "Hit Stage"?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tá super najväčšia hudobná show...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ktorá poskytne čestným hosťom\N30 minút v každom vysielaní?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne, skutočne?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne, skutočne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes je môj šťastný deň!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.72,0:11:58.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem vám kaziť radosť,\Nale tí čestní hostia sme my.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.29,0:12:05.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj! To som ja, malá zlatá Nori!\NRada vás spoznávam!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to má znamenať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne ako som povedala,\Nbudete len sprievodná skupina.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taký malý dezert.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dezert?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.33,0:12:17.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je možné!\NDostal som súhlas od šéfa programu, Yotchana.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prezident je vyššie než Yotchan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže Touma zneužil\Nsvoje postavenie. Ten mazák!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Touma za to nemôže.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.12,0:12:34.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poprosil som ho o to ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.19,0:12:39.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ty si ten zloduch,\Nktorý ju k tomu donútil?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.13,0:12:39.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, daj tie ruky preč z Ryuho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som predsa Ryuichiho bývalý manažér!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne, bývalý!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netvár sa, že si na to zabudol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si pred troma rokmi podviedol\NRyuho a odcestoval s ním do Ameriky!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz si ho odhodil bokom\Na našiel si nového mládenca!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, chudáčik Ryu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To plače kvôli mne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netrep hlúposti!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žartujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:10.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, rada som vás spoznala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.32,0:13:14.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hrozne som chcel s tebou\Nopäť spievať, Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nespomínal som to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som, že vás dobre poznám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A takúto dôležitú vec...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ste mi o tom nepovedali?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.55,0:13:39.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snažím sa pracovať celým svojím srdcom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to stále nestačí,\Npovedzte mi to!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, Sakano, ukľudnite sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to moja chyba,\Nže som vám o tom nepovedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nesplánujem svoju funkciu opustiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.73,0:13:55.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichi s tým prišiel,\Naby sme znovu založili Nittle Grasper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že v ňom precitla nostalgia,\Nkeď videl Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A u mňa tiež.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán president...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.81,0:14:06.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano, už ma tak prosím nevolajte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odteraz som producent,\Npodobne ako vy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.02,0:14:14.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,urobím všetko preto,\Naby bol Nittle Grasper opäť najlepší v Japonsku...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...rovnaký cieľ, ktorý ste si dali vy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odteraz sme konkurencia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes si podivne ticho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Budem so Sakumom v televízii.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je fajn.\NJe predsa tvoj idol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som mnou minule spieval,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bol som tak rozrušený,\Nže som si to neuvedomil,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ale bol úžasný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, takže máš obavy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichi Sakuma je určite úžasný,\Nale si predsa profík.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na pódiu bude Sakuma tvoj rival.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokážeš spievať tak,\Naby si mu stačil?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môj spev...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, konečne budeme\Nv hudobnej show!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Väčšina skupín v iných\Nprogramoch ani navystúpi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Kumagoro je v zovretí!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Kumagoro vracia úder!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.41,0:15:46.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dajme do toho všetko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, dokážeš sa s tým vyrovnať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vystúpiš na rovnakom pódiu\Nako svetoznámy Ryuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.19,0:16:02.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Či sa ti to páči, alebo nie,\Ndiváci vás budú zrovnávať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán K!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichiho poznám veľmi dobre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale vybral som si vás.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš čo to znamená?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.01,0:16:12.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ukáž im, čo dokáže Bad Luck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.66,0:16:32.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a frightened look in my eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.36,0:16:36.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take my impatience
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I toss it to the capricious winds
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.44,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.24,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:42.57,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
