Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.05,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before the sleepy noise...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď to vravíš ty,\Nnaháňa mi to strach.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, ďakujem za spoluprácu!\NDáme si krátku prestávku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.89,0:17:03.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, nebol som dnes úžasný?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.26,0:17:06.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, myslím, že to bol\Nnáš najlepší prednes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Súhlas. Myslím, že máme slušnú\Nšancu konkurovať Nittle Grasperu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol si fantastický!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úžasné, vzrušujúce vystúpenie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daj autogram!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.44,0:17:18.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.61,0:17:23.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, tak vymením ti ho za môj autogram!\NDám ti aj môj prsteň!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám ich plno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, to je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to stváraš, Ryu?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si na rade, rozumieš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:29.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si na rade, rozumieš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si na rade, rozumieš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Noriko, Shuichi je môj kamarát!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Noriko, Shuichi je môj kamarát!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vôbec si sa nezmenil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten svetoznámy Sakuma Ryuichi\Nje tak trochu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trochu mi niekoho pripomína.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kamarát! Povedal, že sme kamaráti!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.70,0:17:51.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úžasne! Úžasne! Sakuma spoznal môj talent?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš, viem čo chceš povedať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na tri...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadišiel čas pre naších čestných hostí!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Po troch rokoch opäť spolu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nittle Grasper!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ich nová pesnička zaznamenala obrovský úspech.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 milióny predaných kópii za 2 dni.\NFantastický rekord.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pýtate sa, čo je na nich také príťažlivé?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Ryuichi je údajne\Nveľmi obľúbený super-talent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odkiaľ berie svoju charizmatickú auru?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes vám predstavia svoju novú pesničku!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.75,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With eyes glinting in the distance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.75,0:18:35.18,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those about to awaken are waiting
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Invited to the night castle
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.12,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Into the empty shell of transient dwellers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.39,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without an exit
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.39,0:18:48.86,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean to endure the shock
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.27,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the point of crumbling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.17,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the lies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.97,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The light I still can't reach and where it's gone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.97,0:19:02.24,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the\Nbrilliantly dancing thoughts
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.24,0:19:06.45,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that the guiding words do not spill over
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.94,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fear the changing times
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.65,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without even an exit
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:17.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Nittle Grapser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.42,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It crumbles apart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Nittle Grapser.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.33,0:19:24.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Videl som ich toľkokrát v televízii.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Táto osoba...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Táto osoba zmenila môj život.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been reborn
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.02,0:19:52.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes alone light up without a smile
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.96,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world you want...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...suddenly turns to ashes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There will still be miracles
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The light I can't reach and where it's gone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.20,0:20:06.47,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the\Nbrilliantly dancing thoughts
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.47,0:20:10.61,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that the guiding words do not spill over
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.41,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fear the changing times
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.78,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace me gently, hold me forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.45,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More, so you'll even break my soul
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.52,0:20:35.85,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst a noisy crowd of people
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.52,0:20:35.85,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nigiyaka na hitogomi ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.59,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The murmured words melt away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.59,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokeru tsubuyaki ga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.09,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered at my feet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.09,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ashimoto ni chirabatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.72,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are memories that become blurred by it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.72,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nijimaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.17,0:20:55.71,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wander aimlessly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.17,0:20:55.71,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi aruku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:59.30,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the brilliant lights of the town
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:59.30,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machi no kagayaki wa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.58,0:21:02.94,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glaring one way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.88,0:21:08.51,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Illuminate me, on the verge of freezing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.88,0:21:08.51,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoesou na boku o terasu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.52,0:21:15.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cold time brings dreams from the skies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.52,0:21:15.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumetai toki ga yume o furaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.49,0:21:20.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they slip through my fingers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.49,0:21:20.16,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kono te no naka o surinukete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.16,0:21:24.97,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting my wishes, when I wake up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.16,0:21:24.97,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negai kazoe mezameta toki ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.97,0:21:33.01,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are there in the wavering vision
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.97,0:21:33.01,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yureru maboroshi ni kimi ga utsuru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.01,0:21:38.61,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A faint silhouette that guides me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.01,0:21:38.61,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boku o michibiku kasuka na shiruetto
